Serious game bugs:

There are a number of bugs in this game.  Until we can fix them,
please try and work around them.  Anyone found deliberately crashing
the game may lose wiz privs.  Anyone found reporting a serious bug
(previously unknown :) may be promoted.


(2) having add_action("exit") can crash the game.

(3) calling set_heart_beat(1) with no heart_beat(){} function can
crash the game.

(4) ^d in the middle of player input can crash the game

(5) so will too much input

These bug notices are temporary until they're fixed...
